----------------QUESTION 3----------------------------

mysql> UPDATE PRODUCT SET price=price+(price*(2/100));
Query OK, 5 rows affected (0.06 sec)
Rows matched: 5  Changed: 5  Warnings: 0

mysql> select *from PRODUCT;
+-----+--------+--------+
| pid | pname  | price  |
+-----+--------+--------+
| 101 | PEN    | 100.00 |
| 102 | BOOK   |  60.00 |
| 103 | BOX    |  30.00 |
| 104 | PENCIL |  60.00 |
| 105 | SCALE  |  50.00 |
+-----+--------+--------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)




-------------new table--------------------




mysql> select *from PRODUCT;
+-----+--------+--------+
| pid | pname  | price  |
+-----+--------+--------+
| 101 | PEN    | 102.00 |
| 102 | BOOK   |  61.20 |
| 103 | BOX    |  30.60 |
| 104 | PENCIL |  61.20 |
